{"tid":195462,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人解釋下脆辣、巴辣、脆香、香辣有咩分別？","createTime":"2017-04-10T15:20:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-10T16:23:53.000Z","uid":88544,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fade4d03d0877fc2be968d8b5962203a250925b4","tid":195462,"uid":88544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T15:20:25.000Z","msg":"自問我食快餐大，細個放學就去唔同快餐店食，最鐘意係炸野，但係<br />\n<br />\n脆辣：（以雞腿包為例）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/10/231105_2b837ebd9141a2a9d4c758d73a3db869.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F10%2F231105_2b837ebd9141a2a9d4c758d73a3db869.jpg&h=22f0ac1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴辣：（雞翼）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/10/231240_de83d15b4473c3ca70072f2a16ee9d52.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F10%2F231240_de83d15b4473c3ca70072f2a16ee9d52.jpg&h=bcdd30ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n脆香：（雞翼，到而家都唔撚明點解係辣）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/10/231355_6c8fe638c0aea5fd0adfd8467cb089eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F10%2F231355_6c8fe638c0aea5fd0adfd8467cb089eb.jpg&h=5ac7ee8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香辣：（香辣脆雞，官方名來唔係鳩up）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/10/231542_41b2f75d9217d0c1b3aadfbe60dc0228.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F10%2F231542_41b2f75d9217d0c1b3aadfbe60dc0228.jpg&h=a1de39c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到底呢四個差唔撚多既炸雞，點解可以有唔同名，ok你可以講邊個好食啲邊個服務好啲，咁係人都知kfc既炸雞又乾又放得耐，我唔想討論呢個。kfc偏偏就係有巴辣同香辣，而老麥就避開左呢兩個名，好地地一隻辣雞翼走去叫脆香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無行家解釋下？仲有除左呢啲辣仲有乜鳩辣？"},{"pid":"7dd30733a4b741122ef12ad10f051b24ad20dfd0","tid":195462,"uid":73202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T15:22:38.000Z","msg":"你份人真係好鬼巴辣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4e51f59fe5a9ba180d2d68f7651886ae6521b33","tid":195462,"uid":88544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T15:23:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你份人真係好鬼巴辣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我=辣撚殺"},{"pid":"4476c2b4de9c9373346c2da3aa7f0504cc8512b4","tid":195462,"uid":55614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T15:25:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你份人真係好鬼巴辣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你份人真係好鬼脆香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2d1161eb1bd0cb1482d5efa197346d0db70b75f","tid":195462,"uid":18279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T15:25:52.000Z","msg":"鳩改嘅名點解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f421338d97d278f078c1924646b1fef99493b99","tid":195462,"uid":88544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T15:26:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鳩改嘅名點解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n俾啲科學精神"},{"pid":"21f314a004578a754df31d05fa6e6e35772c6955","tid":195462,"uid":40867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T15:30:21.000Z","msg":"巴西？？？"},{"pid":"4eddde7b1079cce37ba4af3d7488a8dea9529b57","tid":195462,"uid":51334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T15:32:25.000Z","msg":"咪都係雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"540958acfd53b197c839c4fd0a0d3523902374b3","tid":195462,"uid":88544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T15:33:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咪都係雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌完都要回味"},{"pid":"af012bc823f294250d70528071ad33aa561cde82","tid":195462,"uid":86943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T15:33:51.000Z","msg":"脆辣：皮厚+辣，舊雞辣<br />\n脆香：皮厚，舊雞辣<br />\n巴辣："},{"pid":"f93b62117e1c9335ff726ddc920e6c8997ae994b","tid":195462,"uid":86943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T15:34:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>脆辣：皮厚+辣，舊雞辣<br />\n脆香：皮厚，舊雞辣<br />\n巴辣：凍水皮，個皮唔辣舊雞辣<br />\n香辣：薄皮，舊雞辣</blockquote>"},{"pid":"56c312c3a8ad0d9a36d14cd1d068a45dd7fa196f","tid":195462,"uid":86943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T15:35:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>脆辣：皮厚+辣，舊雞辣<br />\n脆香：皮厚，舊雞辣<br />\n香辣：凍水皮，個皮唔辣舊雞辣<br />\n巴辣：薄皮，舊雞辣</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n香辣巴辣掉轉咗"},{"pid":"844727317c0bff95729805204828e70485487a3b","tid":195462,"uid":88544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T15:40:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>脆辣：皮厚+辣，舊雞辣<br />\n脆香：皮厚，舊雞辣<br />\n香辣：凍水皮，個皮唔辣舊雞辣<br />\n巴辣：薄皮，舊雞辣</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n香辣巴辣掉轉咗</blockquote><br />\n脆香舊雞其實唔係辣，細個怕辣試過咬走哂啲皮食左肉先食皮，是唔辣的<br />\n<br />\n香辣呢啲辣殺就唔提了，個名都平庸過人<br />\n<br />\n巴辣皮都係辣的"},{"pid":"040473b463189f8ccdb6533814d6c001138b6a8d","tid":195462,"uid":86943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T15:56:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>脆辣：皮厚+辣，舊雞辣<br />\n脆香：皮厚，舊雞辣<br />\n香辣：凍水皮，個皮唔辣舊雞辣<br />\n巴辣：薄皮，舊雞辣</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n香辣巴辣掉轉咗</blockquote><br />\n脆香舊雞其實唔係辣，細個怕辣試過咬走哂啲皮食左肉先食皮，是唔辣的<br />\n<br />\n香辣呢啲辣殺就唔提了，個名都平庸過人<br />\n<br />\n巴辣皮都係辣的</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌錯晒添，返到香港全部試一次先"},{"pid":"bd0017d097f9d3e178d03cd3d9b61ddb1289d6af","tid":195462,"uid":88544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T16:23:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>